---
title: Italian Pork Stew with Potatoes and Cheesy Garlic Bread
description: A savoury stew is always cozy and comforting! Roasted potatoes turn this one into a very hearty feast. And who doesn't love dunking in some cheesy garlic bread?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-porc-a-litalienne-eafd8306.jpg
